en:
Greetings!
My name is Renty :)
I'm created to assist good people in finding accommodation in Yerevan.
My functionality should be simple and clear (that's what my creator thinks), but if you encounter difficulties, feel free to ask a question in support /support
Good luck with your search!

You asked to be silent.
Press the "Start" button for me to speak again.

You've already started me :)
Perhaps you're looking for the menu button? It's right here
üëá
Invalid filter number. Please enter the number of an existing filter.
Do you want to delete another filter?
There are no more filters. Shall we create one?

Which filter would you like to delete?
Write '0' to delete all filters.
To delete something, you need to create something :)
And there are no more filters...
What type of accommodation are you looking for?

Alright. Expect notifications based on your filters.
Write /menu if you need me

Alright. You can take your time to think.
I'll wait for your decision here.
Please enter a number. For example: 1500

Short filter - up to 4 parameters.
Full filter - up to 12 parameters
The minimum price must be less than the maximum
The maximum price must be greater than the minimum
The minimum area must be less than the maximum
The maximum area must be greater than the minimum
You haven't selected a currency yet :)
Do you want to change the currency?
Alright. If I'm needed again, you can summon me through the menu button üëá
The minimum floor cannot be greater than the maximum
Great! The filter has been successfully added. In the last 7 days, there have been @ listings based on your filter. Do you want to add another filter?
Alright. Let's go back to the beginning. Maybe you wanted to change somethingü§î
How many floors do you want in the building?

After creating the filter, you can delete it through the main menu.
Do you confirm the creation of the filter?
How many rooms do you want?

Premium benefits:
1. Unlimited number of listings based on your filters (3 per day without premium)
2. No advertisements
3. Display of statistics (average price based on your filters, comparison with market prices, etc.)
4. Access to more than one listing source

I found another listing for you, but I can't send it without a premium subscription :(
Tomorrow, you will be able to receive up to three listings again! üòä
I'm still here and waiting for your instructions :) Maybe you forgot to continue setting up the filter?
I see that you've stepped away, but you're still in the menu. So I'll start sending your ads for now :)
